== 制作 ==
=== 剧本 ===
{{Quote box |width=30em|bgcolor=#c6dbf7|quote=“埃里克·罗斯的剧本基本上脱离原著。我们沉迷于原著的两大元素，让爱情故事占主体，奇幻冒险当配菜。而影片中，阿甘是位极为体面的人物，始终信守诺言，做事没有安排，除了珍妮、母亲和上帝，对任何事情都没有主见。”|source=—导演[[罗伯特·泽米基斯|罗伯特·泽米基斯]]<ref name="BookChanges"/>}}
影片改编自1986年[[溫斯頓·葛魯姆|溫斯頓·葛魯姆]][[阿甘正传_(小说)|同名小说]]，主角均为福雷斯特·甘。然而，电影主要侧重于小说的前十一章，直接跳过小说结尾处阿甘虾业有限公司的成立和与“小阿甘”的团聚。除了跳过小说的部分内容，电影还新增了部分内容，比如小时候腿部装支架的阿甘跑遍全美国<ref name="MoviesBook">{{cite news|last=Delarte|first=Alonso|title=Movies By The Book: Forrest Gump|work=Bob's Poetry Magazine|format=PDF|date=February 2004|url=http://bobspoetry.com/Bobs01Fe.pdf|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327090919/http://bobspoetry.com/Bobs01Fe.pdf|archivedate=2009-03-27|page=24|accessdate=2009-07-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

小说中阿甘的核心特征和性格也被改变，除了其他，阿甘的电影角色中缺少[[学者症候群|自闭症天才]]的描写——而在小说中，阿甘在大学里踢足球，不能做手工和健身，但在高级物理课上取得突出成绩，让他成为教练，以满足大学的需求<ref name="MoviesBook"/>。小说还提到阿甘是[[宇航员|宇航员]]、[[职业摔跤手|职业摔跤手]]和[[棋手|棋手]]<ref name="MoviesBook"/>。

在[[罗伯特·泽米基斯|罗伯特·泽米基斯]]被选中前，他和另一位导演[[特里·吉列姆|特里·吉列姆]]都有机会执导本片，但吉列姆拒绝了导演的邀请<ref name="GilliamDirect">{{cite web|last=Plume|first=Kenneth|url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/644/644724p1.html|title=Gilliam on Grimm|publisher=IGN|page=3|date=2005-08-24|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tdcP3CHA?url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/644/644724p1.html|archivedate=2010-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[巴里·索南菲尔德|巴里·索南菲尔德]]也受到青睐，但却改去导演《[[亚当斯一家的价值观|亚当斯一家的价值观]]》<ref name="BarryDirect">{{cite news|last=Fretts|first=Bruce|title=Get Barry|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,299341,00.html|work=Entertainment Weekly|page=2|date=1995-11-03|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tdcScZ2H?url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,299341,00.html|archivedate=2010-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 摄制 ===
影片于1993年8月开始摄制，同年12月结束<ref name="FilminDates">{{cite news|last=McKenna|first=Kristine|authorlink=Kristine McKenna|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/access/60281832.html?dids=60281832:60281832&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Dec+19%2C+1993&author=KRISTINE+McKENNA&pub=Los+Angeles+Times+%28pre-1997+Fulltext%29&desc=Cover+Story+He%27s+Serious+About+This+One+For+Tom+Hanks%2C+it%27s+been+a+long+ride+from+%60Splash%27+to+%60Philadelphia%2C%27+in+which+the+likable+comedy+actor+plays+an+AIDS+patient+who%27s+fired+from+his+job.+What+made+him+take+the+leap%3F+It+has+a+lot+to+do+with+what+he%27s+done+so+far%2C+the+times+and%2C+well%2C+life&pqatl=google|title=He's Serious About This One For Tom Hanks, it's been a long ride from 'Splash' to 'Philadelphia,' in which the likable comedy actor plays an AIDS patient who's fired from his job|work=Los Angeles Times|format=Fee required|date=1993-12-19|accessdate=2010-06-13}}</ref>。大多数场景在[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]取景，但主要是在附近的[[南卡罗来纳州|南卡罗来纳州]][[博福特_(南卡罗来纳州)|博福特]]和维吉尼亚州部分沿岸地区取景<ref name="HankSign">{{cite news|last=Mal|first=Vincent|title=Show Some Gumption Hanks Excels in Tale of a Simple Man's Brushes with Fame|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=VP&p_theme=vp&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EAFF785EECC284D&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|format=Fee required|work=[[The_Virginian-Pilot|The Virginian-Pilot]]|date=1994-07-06|accessdate=2009-07-01}}</ref>，包括[[蓝岭山行车通道|蓝岭山行车通道]]的跑步镜头<ref>[http://www.indianagazette.com/a_news/article_6088508b-000c-5c86-a60e-5ea14a1d9112.html Must-see sites abound along Blue Ridge Parkway – The Indiana Gazette Online: Indiana County Area News] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130126081418/http://www.indianagazette.com/a_news/article_6088508b-000c-5c86-a60e-5ea14a1d9112.html |date=2013-01-26 }}. Indianagazette.com (June 12, 2011). Retrieved on March 7, 2013.</ref>。虚构城镇的市区部分则是[[南卡罗来纳州|南卡罗来纳州]][[瓦恩维尔_(南卡罗来纳州)|瓦恩维尔]]<ref>[http://www.movie-locations.com/movies/f/ForrestGump.html Film locations for Forrest Gump (1994)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.movie-locations.com/movies/f/ForrestGump.html |date=20190806231350 }}. Movie-locations.com. Retrieved on March 7, 2013.</ref>。阿甘在越南战场火线下跑步的场景，则在南卡罗来纳州弗里普岛取景<ref>{{cite news|last=Smith|first=Katherine|title=Island getaway is motion-picture perfect|work=St. Petersburg Times|url=http://www.sptimes.com/2004/06/27/Travel/Island_getaway_is_mot.shtml|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5z86Y7fc7?url=http://www.sptimes.com/2004/06/27/Travel/Island_getaway_is_mot.shtml|archivedate=2011-06-02|access-date=2012-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他取景地包括[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]][[阿什维尔_(北卡罗来纳州)|阿什维尔]]的[[比尔特莫庄园|比尔特莫庄园]]和北卡罗来纳州[[布恩|布恩]]的蓝岭大道。最引人著名地方是[[祖父山|祖父山]]的一段路名为“阿甘弯道<ref>Grandfather Mountain audio tour</ref>”。阿甘一家的屋子在南卡罗来纳州[[雅马西_(南卡罗来纳州)|雅马西]]附近的[[康巴黑河|康巴黑河]]搭建，附近的土地用作珍妮的家以及越南的战场<ref name="DVDProdDesign">{{cite video|title=Forrest Gump-(Building the World of Gump: Production Design)|medium=DVD|publisher=[[Paramount_Pictures|Paramount Pictures]]|date=2001-08-28}}</ref>，越南场景种了20棵棕榈树<ref name="DVDProdDesign"/>。影片开头阿甘讲述他一生的故事，是在[[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]][[萨凡纳_(佐治亚州)|萨凡纳]]的齐佩瓦广场巴士站长凳。萨凡纳周边地区也用来取景，包括理查德·V.伍兹纪念大桥取景的跑步镜头，以及在萨凡纳西湾街接受媒体采访的场景<ref name="DVDProdDesign"/>。大学校园多数取景于[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[南加州大学|南加州大学]]。阿甘首次跑步横跨大西洋是在[[缅因州|缅因州]][[克莱德港_(缅因州)|克莱德港]]的马歇尔灯塔。

=== 特效 ===
[[File:ForrestGumpwithJFKScreenshot.jpg|thumb]]总统。影片中，多种特效被用来将汤姆·汉克斯（阿甘）融入各种历史人物和事件及旧镜头中。]]
肯·罗尔斯敦（Ken Ralston）的团队在[[光影魔幻工業|光影魔幻工業]]为影片制作特效。影片中阿甘與當時名人握手的場景，採用了[[電腦成像|CGI]]技术。汉克斯首次戴参考标识面对蓝幕拍戏，以便调整档案影片<ref name="DVDEyes1">{{cite video|title=Forrest Gump-(Through the eyes of Forrest Gump)|medium=DVD|publisher=[[Paramount_Pictures|Paramount Pictures]]|time=12:29|date=2001-08-28}}</ref>。为了录下历史人物的声音，用上了双语音，新的对话用特效改变嘴部的运动<ref name="BookChanges">{{cite news|last=Mills|first=Bart|title=In 'Forrest Gump,' Historical Figures Speak for Themselves|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/24184772.html?dids=24184772:24184772&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jul+08%2C+1994&author=Bart+Mills.+Special+to+the+Tribune.&pub=Chicago+Tribune+%28pre-1997+Fulltext%29&desc=IN+%60FORREST+GUMP%2C%27+HISTORICAL+FIGURES+SPEAK+FOR+THEMSELVES&pqatl=google|format=Fee required|work=Chicago Tribune|date=1994-07-08|accessdate=2010-06-13}}</ref>。档案影片用上了[[色键|色键]]、[[图像变形|图像变形]]、[[影响变形|影响变形]]、[[转描机技术|转描机技术]]等技术，配合汉克斯動作。

在越南戰爭的一處場景中，阿甘背著布巴逃離凝固汽油彈的襲擊。要創建這種效果，要用上特技演員來合成。隨後，漢克斯和威廉姆森被拍攝，威廉姆森由電纜線支撐，漢克斯帶著他跑。之後再攝製爆炸，爆炸前將演員數位化加入。噴氣式戰鬥機和凝固汽油彈罐也用CGI補充<ref name="DVDVietnam">{{cite video|title=Forrest Gump-(Seeing is Believing: The Visual Effects of Forrest Gump-Vietnam)|medium=DVD|publisher=[[Paramount_Pictures|Paramount Pictures]]|date=2001-08-28}}</ref>。

CGI技术去除演员加里·辛尼斯的双腿，以迎合他截肢的特点。加里的双腿用蓝色布料包裹，便于特效团队逐帧描绘他的双腿。因此，加里要坐轮椅来支持双腿，提高自己<ref name="DVDLegs">{{cite video|title=Forrest Gump-(Seeing is Believing: The Visual Effects of Forrest Gump-Lt. Dan's Legs)|medium=DVD|publisher=[[Paramount_Pictures|Paramount Pictures]]|date=2001-08-28}}</ref>。

阿甘在[[林肯紀念堂|林肯紀念堂]]水池[[和平集會|和平集會]]碰見珍妮的場景，用上影片效果來創建一大群人<ref name="DVDEnhanReal">{{cite video|title=Forrest Gump-(Seeing is Believing: The Visual Effects of Forrest Gump-Enhancing Reality)|medium=DVD|publisher=[[Paramount_Pictures|Paramount Pictures]]|date=2001-08-28}}</ref>。兩天的拍攝用上約1500名群眾演員，每個連續的鏡頭都要臨時演員重新排列，進入遠離機位的不同象限。在電腦的幫助下，又另外打造出好幾十萬人<ref name="HankSign"/><ref name="DVDEnhanReal"/>。

== 发行 ==
=== 专业评价 ===
本片评价普遍积极。评论聚合网站[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]基于79条评论，给予本片71%的积极评价<ref name="RTFresh">{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/forrest_gump/|title=Forrest Gump|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-09-05}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]基于19条主流影评人的评价，给本片打出82分（100分满分）<ref name="Metacritic">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/forrest-gump |title=Forrest Gump|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2009-07-01}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「A+」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/why-cinemascore-matters-box-office-225563|title=Why CinemaScore Matters for Box Office|author=Pamela McClintock|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2011-08-19|accessdate=2016-09-14|archive-date=2014-05-10|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6PTUrtDVN?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/why-cinemascore-matters-box-office-225563|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

几位影评人赞赏影片的剧情。《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的[[罗杰·艾伯特|罗杰·艾伯特]]写道：“我此前从未见过一部像《阿甘正传》的电影，有些人认为影片冒着看起来更传统的风险，但我正想尝试。我猜这是一部喜剧片，或许是一场话剧，或许是一个梦。[[埃里克·罗斯|埃里克·罗斯]]的剧本具备现代小说的复杂性。剧情喜感和悲情相互交融的平衡令人惊叹，充斥笑声之余带来沉思……真是一部神奇的电影<ref name="EbertReview">{{cite news|last=Ebert|first=Roger|authorlink=Roger Ebert|title=Forrest Gump|url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/19940706/REVIEWS/407060301/1023|work=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]]|date=1994-07-06|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tdcVK1ue?url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F19940706%2FREVIEWS%2F407060301%2F1023|archivedate=2010-10-21|deadurl=no}}</ref>。”《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的托德·麦卡锡认为电影“在所有层面都做得很出色，困难技术的处理让人倍感亲切，带着轻微哀求的故事演绎细腻均匀完胜史诗片<ref name="VarietyReview">{{cite news|last=McCarthy|first=Todd|title=Forrest Gump|url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117487968/ |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=1994-07-10|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5tdcXZ7y4|archivedate=2010-10-20| deadurl = no }}</ref>。”本片也收到几位著名影评人的批评。《[[纽约客|纽约客]]》的[[安东尼·雷恩|安东尼·雷恩]]批评电影“热情明智得让人非常反感<ref name="NYorkerReview">{{cite news|last=Lane|first=Anthony|authorlink=Anthony Lane|title=Forrest Gump|url=http://www.newyorker.com/arts/reviews/film/forrest_gump_zemeckis|work=[[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tdcaDuSJ?url=http://www.newyorker.com/arts/reviews/film/forrest_gump_zemeckis|archivedate=2010-10-21|deadurl=no}}</ref>”。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的[[欧文·葛莱伯曼|欧文·葛莱伯曼]]称电影“将过去几十年来的喧嚣削减成一个虚拟现实的主题公园：婴儿潮版[[美国迪士尼|美国迪士尼]]<ref name="EWReviewC">{{cite news|last=Gleiberman|first=Owen|title=Forrest Gump (1994)|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,302943,00.html|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=1994-07-15|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tdccuaCJ?url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,302943,00.html|archivedate=2010-10-21|deadurl=no}}</ref>。”

影评人对主角的看法不一。阿甘被拿来给各种角色和人物进行比较，包括[[哈克贝利·费恩历险记|哈克贝利·费恩]]、[[比尔·克林顿|比尔·克林顿]]和[[罗纳德·里根|罗纳德·里根]]<ref name="GumpHuck">{{cite news|last=Hinson|first=Hal|title=Forrest Gump, Our National Folk Zero|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/review97/fforrestgump1.htm|work=The Washington Post|date=1994-08-14|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tdcgBBlq?url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/review97/fforrestgump1.htm|archivedate=2010-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="GumpClinton">{{cite news|last=Rich|first=Frank|title=The Gump From Hope|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1994/07/21/opinion/journal-the-gump-from-hope.html|work=The New York Times|date=1994-07-21|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tdcil4Kj?url=http://www.nytimes.com/1994/07/21/opinion/journal-the-gump-from-hope.html|archivedate=2010-10-21|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="WorldTime">{{cite news|last=Corliss|first=Richard|author2=Julie Grace|author3=Martha Smilgis|title=The World According to Gump|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,981196-2,00.html|work=Time|date=1994-08-01|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tdcktpoX?url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,981196-2,00.html|archivedate=2010-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。彼得·卓木认为阿甘扮演着一位“社会调解员和救赎不同时段的代理人<ref name="WangStruggle">{{cite journal|last=Wang|first=Jennifer Hyland|title="A Struggle of Contending Stories": Race, Gender, and Political Memory in Forrest Gump|journal=Cinema Journal|url=http://proquest.umi.com.libproxy.sdsu.edu/pqdweb?index=0&did=1068720901&SrchMode=2&sid=1&Fmt=6&VInst=PROD&VType=PQD&RQT=309&VName=PQD&TS=1246568407&clientId=17862|format=PDF|pages=92–102|volume=39|issue=3|date=Spring 2000|accessdate=2009-07-02|doi=10.1353/cj.2000.0009}}</ref>。”《[[滚石|滚石]]》的[[彼得·崔维斯|彼得·崔维斯]]称阿甘的一切“是我们所佩服的美国人形象——诚实、勇敢、忠诚<ref name="RollStone">{{cite news|last=Travers|first=Peter|authorlink=Peter Travers|title=Forrest Gump|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/movie/5948073/review/5948074/forrest_gump|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|date=2000-12-08|accessdate=2009-07-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080622125023/http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/movie/5948073/review/5948074/forrest_gump|archivedate=2008-06-22|deadurl=yes}}</ref>”。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》评论员珍妮特·马斯林称阿甘是“空心人”，“沾沾自喜于他那幸福的愚昧，热情的拥抱是没有内涵体现<ref name="MaslinGump">{{cite news|last=Burr|first=Ty|title=Loss of innocence: 'Forrest Gump' at 10|url=http://www.boston.com/news/globe/living/articles/2004/06/20/loss_of_innocence_forrest_gump_at_10/|work=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]|date=1994-06-20|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tdcpAjm3?url=http://www.boston.com/news/globe/living/articles/2004/06/20/loss_of_innocence_forrest_gump_at_10/|archivedate=2010-10-21|deadurl=no|quote=Film critic Pauline Kael came out of retirement to bash the film on a book tour; by year's end, New York Times reviewer Janet Maslin had gone from mildly praising the film in her initial review to putting it on her worst of 1994 list, describing Forrest as a "hollow man" who's 'self-congratulatory in his blissful ignorance, warmly embraced as the embodiment of absolutely nothing.'}}</ref>。”《帕洛阿尔托周报》的马克·文森提称主角是“可怜的傀儡，脸上沾着生命的馅饼，还若有所思地舔着手指<ref name="PaloAltoGump">{{cite news|last=Vincenti|first=Marc|title=Forrest Gump|url=http://www.paloaltoonline.com/movies/reviews/Forrest-Gump?review_id=655|work=[[Palo_Alto_Weekly|Palo Alto Weekly]]|date=August 1994|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tdcuI4so?url=http://www.paloaltoonline.com/movies/reviews/Forrest-Gump?review_id=655|archivedate=2010-10-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。”布鲁斯·凯因和杰拉德·马斯特在电影史教材中，指出本片暗喻着对愁绪的美化，代表着一块空白的石板，透过婴儿潮年代生人，预测他们记忆中的事件<ref name="mastshort">{{cite book|last=Mast|first=Gerald|title=A Short History of the Movies: 10th Edition|url=https://archive.org/details/shorthistoryofmo0000mast_j5m2|year=2007|publisher=Longman|location=London}}</ref>。

观众对本片两极分化式的评价常见。《娱乐周刊》2004年写道，“近十年来，影片赚到很大的数目，横扫奥斯卡奖，罗伯特·泽米基斯对20世纪美国的颂歌，仍代表着最能清晰地在沙子上划线的影院之一。一半人把它看作是一部人工流行情景剧，而其他人则在胡言乱语，就像品尝着一盒甜蜜的巧克力那样<ref name="EWStrikeBack">{{cite news|last=Bal|first=Sumeet|author2=Marc Bernardin|author3=Monica Mehta|author4=Joshua Rich|author5=Erin Richter|author6=Michael Sauter|author7=Missy Schwartz|author8=Nancy Sidewater|title=Cry Hard 2 The Readers Strike Back|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,570497,00.html|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2004-01-09|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tdcxFNTj?url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,570497,00.html|archivedate=2010-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

=== 票房表现 ===
本片用5500万美元预算制作，在全美1595家影院上映的首周末，赚得24,450,602美元<ref name="BOXTotal">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=forrestgump.htm|title=Forrest Gump (1994)|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-07-01|archive-date=2013-06-09|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HFbzb537?url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=forrestgump.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影的商业顾问兼编剧[[杰弗里·希尔顿|杰弗里·希尔顿]]观看了电影剧本的样片后，建议制片[[温迪·芬纳曼|温迪·芬纳曼]]将电影营销预算提升两倍，依他的意见，预算随即被提升。本片的周末票房位列第一，险胜上映第四个星期的《[[狮子王|狮子王]]》<ref name="BOXTotal"/>。上映第10周，本片仍保持领先<ref name="WeekendBOX">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekend&id=forrestgump.htm|title=Forrest Gump Weekend Box Office|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-07-01}}</ref>。电影在影院共上映42周，在北美赚取3.297亿美元票房，成为当时第四卖座的电影，仅次于《[[E.T.外星人|E.T.外星人]]》、《[[星際大戰四部曲：曙光乍現|星際大戰四部曲：曙光乍現]]》和《[[侏罗纪公园|侏罗纪公园]]》<ref name="WeekendBOX"/><ref name="DomesticGrosses">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/domestic.htm|title=All Time Box Office Domestic Grosses|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2014-12-31|archive-date=2008-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205064427/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/domestic.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

本片票房花了66天便超越2.5亿，是票房最快增长至1亿、2亿、3亿美元大关的派拉蒙电影（在当时上映而言）<ref name="Fastest100">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/fastest.htm?page=100&p=.htm|title=Fastest to $100 million|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-07-01|archive-date=2019-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190830125641/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/fastest.htm?page=100&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Fastest200">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/fastest.htm?page=200&p=.htm|title=Fastest to $200 million|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-07-01}}</ref><ref name="Fastest300">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/fastest.htm?page=300&p=.htm|title=Fastest to $300 million|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-07-01}}</ref>。本片在全球斩获6.77亿票房<ref name="BOXTotal"/>。即使有着可观的收入，电影仍被称为是“成功的失败”——由于发行商和参展商的花销高昂，派拉蒙亏损6200万美元，管理層意识到谈妥生意的必要性<ref>McDonald, Paul, and Janet Wasko. The Contemporary Hollywood Film Industry. Malden: Blackwell, 2008. Pg:79 #</ref>。然而，跟好莱坞的核算也有牵涉的是，费用的膨胀使得分红尽量减少。

